translations: n.苏禄裙；苏禄人（菲律宾的苏禄群岛人）

phrs.translation: 苏禄省, 菲律宾苏禄, 苏禄岛
苏鲁田光, 中扮演光·苏鲁
苏禄王朝, 苏禄苏丹国
锡亚西岛和卡加延苏禄

sentences.sentence: A city of Malaysia in northern Borneo on Sandakan Harbor, an inlet of the Sulu Sea.
sentences.translation: 山打根马来西亚一城市，位于北婆罗洲的山打根港，它是苏禄海的一个小水湾。

sentences.sentence: Even then I think Sulu was checking out Go Fug Yourself. (See the top 10 gadgets of 2009.)
sentences.translation: 即使这种时刻，我觉得苏鲁也是在看明星八卦网站。

sentences.sentence: Plumes of sediment from overburden piles enter the Sulu Sea along the northern and eastern coastline of the island.
sentences.translation: 从覆盖的沉积物羽流进桩沿岛的北部和东部海岸线的苏禄海。
